quran[118]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Yaqeenan falaah payi hai iman laney walon ne jo
  23,2,Apni namaz mein khushu ikhtiyar karte hain (Salat with humility)
  23,3,Laghviyat (vain things) se door rehte hain
  23,4,Zakaat ke tareeqe par aamil hotey hain
  23,5,Apni sharmgaahon ki hifazat karte hain
  23,6,Siwaye apni biwiyon ke aur un auraton ke jo unki milk e yameen mein hon (right hand posseses) ke unpar (mehfooz na rakhne mein) woh qabil e malamat nahin hain
  23,7,Albatta jo uske alawa kuch aur chahein wahi zyadati karne waley hain
  23,8,Apni amanaton (trusts) aur apne ahad o paiman (promises) ka paas rakhte hain
  23,9,Aur apni namazon ki muhafizat (hifazat) karte hain
  23,10,Yahi log woh waris hain
  23,11,Jo miraas mein firdous payenge aur usmein hamesha rahenge
  23,12,Humne Insaan ko mitti ke saatt (essence of clay) se banaya
  23,13,Phir usey ek mehfooz jaga tapki hui boondh mein tabdeel kiya
  23,14,"Phir us boondh ko lothday ki shakal di, phir lothday ko boti bana diya, phir boti ki haddiyan (bones) banayin, phir haddiyon par gosht chadhaya. Phir usey ek dusri hi makhlooq bana khada kiya. Pas bada hi ba-barakat hai Allah, sab karigaron se accha kaarigar(creator)"
  23,15,Phir iske baad tumko zaroor marna hai
  23,16,Phir qayamat ke roz yaqeenan tum uthaye jaogey
  23,17,"Aur tumhare upar humne saat (seven) raastey banaye, takhleeq ke kaam se hum kuch na-balad na thay (We are never unmindful of (our) Creation"
  23,18,Aur aasmaan se humne theek hisaab ke mutabiq ek khaas miqdar mein pani utara aur usko zameen mein thehara diya. Hum usey jis tarah chahein gayab kar sakte hain
  23,19,"Phir is pani ke zariye se humne tumhare liye khajoor aur angoor ke baagh paida kardiye, tumhare liye in baaghon mein bahut se lazeez phal hain aur unsey tum rozi haasil karte ho"
  23,20,"Aur woh darakht bhi humne paida kiya jo Tur-e-seena (mount sinai) se nikalta hai, teil (oil) bhi liye huey ugta hai aur khane walon ke liye saalan bhi"
  23,21,"Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumhare liye maweshiyon mein bhi ek sabaq hai unke paithon (bellies) mein jo kuch hai usi mein se ek cheez hum tumhein pilatey hain, aur tumhare liye unmein bahut se dusre faiyde bhi hain"
  23,22,Unko tum khate ho aur unpar aur kashtiyon par sawaar bhi kiye jatey ho
  23,23,"Humne Nooh ko uski qaum ki taraf bheja, usne kaha “ aey meri qaum ke logon, Allah ki bandagi karo, uske siwa tumhare liye koi aur mabood nahin hai, kya tum darte nahin ho?”"
  23,24,Uski qaum ke jin sardaaron ne maanne se inkar kiya woh kehne lagey ke “yeh shaks kuch nahin hai magar ek bashar(Insaan) tum hi jaisa. Iski garz yeh hai ke tumpar bartari (superiority) haasil karey. Allah ko agar bhejna hota to farishtey bhejta.Yeh baat to humne kabhi apne baap dada ke waqton mein suni hi nahin ( ke bashar Rasool bankar aaye)
  23,25,"Kuch nahin , bas is aadmi ko zara junoon lahaq(possessed) ho gaya hai, kuch muddat aur dekhlo [ ( shayad ifaqa ho jaaye)( may be he is cured)]”"
  23,26,"Nooh ne kaha “parwardigar, in logon ne jo meri takzeeb ki hai ispar ab tu hi meri nusrat farma.”"
  23,27,"Humne uspar wahee ki ke “hamari nigrani mein aur hamari wahee ke mutabiq kashti (ark) tayyar kar. Phir jab hamara hukum aa jaye aur tannur ubal paday to har qisam ke jaanwaron mein se ek ek joda lekar usmein sawaar ho ja, aur apne ehal o ayaal ko bhi saath le, siwai unke jinke khilaf pehle faisla ho chuka hai, aur zaalimon ke maamle mein mujhse kuch na kehna, yeh ab garq (doob/ drown) honay waley hain"
  23,28,"Phir jab tu apne saathiyon sameth kashti par sawar ho jaye to keh, shukar hai us khuda ka jisne humein zaalim logon se nijaat di"
  23,29,"Aur keh, parwardigar, mujhko barakat wali jagah utaar aur tu behtareen jagah dene wala hai.”"
  23,30,Is qissey mein badi nishaniyan hain aur aazmaish to hum karke hi rehte hain
  23,31,Inke baad humne ek dusre daur ki qaum uthayi
  23,32,"Phir un mein khud unhi ki qaum ka ek Rasool bheja ( jisne unhein dawat di) ke Allah ki bandagi karo, tumhare liye uske siwa koi aur maabood nahin hai, kya tum darte nahin ho"
  23,33,"Uski qaum ke jin sardaron ne maanne se inkar kiya aur aakhirat ki peshi ko jhutlaya, jinko humne duniya ki zindagi mein aasuda kar rakkha tha, woh kehne lagey “ye shaks kuch nahin hai magar ek bashar tum hi jaisa, jo kuch tum khate ho wahi yeh khata hai aur jo kuch tum peete ho wahi yeh peeta hai"
  23,34,Ab agar tumne apne hi jaise ek bashar ki itaat qabool karli to tum ghatay hi mein rahey
  23,35,Yeh tumhein ittila deta hai ke jab tum mar kar mitti ho jaogey aur haddiyon ka panjar reh jaogey us waqt tum (qabaron se) nikale jaogey
  23,36,"Baeed (far/Impossible), bilkul baeed(Impossible) hai yeh wada jo tumse kiya jaa raha hai"
  23,37,Zindagi kuch nahin hai magar bas yahi duniya ki zindagi. Yahin humko marna aur jeena hai aur hum hargiz uthaye janey waley nahin hain
  23,38,Yeh shaks khuda ke naam par mehaz jhoot ghadh raha hai aur hum kabhi iske maanne waley nahin hain.”
  23,39,"Rasool ne kaha “parwardigar , in logon ne jo meri takzeeb ki hai, ispar ab tu hi meri nusrat farma”"
  23,40,Jawab mein irshad hua “qareeb hai woh waqt jab yeh apne kiye par pachtayenge”
  23,41,Aakhir e kaar theek theek haqq ke mutabiq ek hungama e azeem ne unko aa liya aur humne inko kachra bana kar phenk diya. Door ho zaalim qaum
  23,42,Phir humne unke baad dusri qaumein uthayi
  23,43,Koi qaum na apne waqt se pehle khatam hui aur na uske baad thehar saki
  23,44,"Phir humne pai dar pai apne Rasool bheje. Jis qaum ke paas bhi uska Rasool aaya, usne usey jhutlaya, aur hum ek ke baad ek qaum ko halaak karte chale gaye hatta ke unko bas afsana hi bana kar choda, phitkar un logon par jo iman nahin laatey"
  23,45,Phir humne Moosa aur uske bhai Haroon ko apni nishaniyon aur khuli sanad ke saath Firoun aur uske ayaan sultanat ki taraf bheja
  23,46,Magar unhon ne takabbur (arrogance) kiya aur badi dunki li
  23,47,Kehne lage “Kya hum apne hi jaise do aadmiyon par iman le aayein? Aur aadmi bhi woh jinki qaum hamari bandi (ghulam) hai”
  23,48,Pas unhon ne dono ko jhutla diya aur halaak honay walon mein jaa miley
  23,49,Aur Moosa ko humne kitaab ata farmayi taa-ke log ussey rehnumayi haasil karein
  23,50,Aur Ibne Maryam aur uski maa ko humne ek nishani banaya aur unko ek sateh murtafa (shelter on a plateau) par rakkha jo itminaan ki jagah thi aur chashme usmein jaari thay
  23,51,"Aey paigambaron, khao paak cheezein aur amal karo saleh, tum jo kuch bhi karte ho, main usko khoob jaanta hoon"
  23,52,"Aur yeh tumhari yeh ummat ek hi ummat hai aur main tumhara Rubb hoon, pas mujhi se tum daro"
  23,53,"Magar baad mein logon ne apne deen (religion) ko aapas mein tukde tukde karliya, har giroh ke paas jo kuch hai usi mein woh magan hai"
  23,54,"Accha, to chodo inhein, doobey rahein apni gaflat mein ek waqt e khaas tak"
  23,55,Kya yeh samajhte hain ke hum jo inhein maal o aulad se madad diye jaa rahey hain
  23,56,"To goya inhein bhalaiyan dene mein sargarm hain? Nahin, asal maamle ka inhein shaour nahin hai"
  23,57,Jo apne Rubb ke khauf se darey rehte hain
  23,58,Jo Rubb ki aayat par iman latey hain
  23,59,Jo apne Rubb ke saath kisi ko shareek nahin karte
  23,60,Aur jinka haal yeh hai ke detay hain jo kuch bhi detay hain aur dil unke is khayal se kaampte rehte hain ke humein apne Rubb ki taraf palatna hai
  23,61,Bhalaiyon ki taraf daudne waley aur sabaqat karke unhein paa lene waley to dar-haqeeqat woh log hain
  23,62,"Hum kisi shaks ko uski maqdart (taaqat) se zyada ki takleef nahin detay aur humare paas ek kitaab hai jo (har ek ka haal) theek theek bata dene wali hai, aur logon par zulm bahr-haal nahin kiya jayega"
  23,63,Magar yeh log is maamle se be-khabar hain aur inke aamal bhi is tareeqe se ( jiska upar zikr kiya gaya hai) mukhtalif hain. Woh apne yeh karoot kiye chale jayenge
  23,64,Yahan tak ke jab hum unke ayyashon (affluent ones /aasuda haal) ko azaab mein pakad lenge to phir woh dakrana shuru kar denge (begin to bellow /cry)
  23,65,"Ab bandh karo apni fariyad o fugaan, hamari taraf se ab koi madad tumhein nahin milni"
  23,66,Meri aayat sunayi jati thi to tum (Rasool ki aawaz sunte hi) ultay paon bhaag nikalte thay
  23,67,"Apne ghamand mein usko khatir hi mein na latey thay,apne chaoupalon (meeting places) mein unpar baatein chaant-te (ridiculed him) aur bakwas kiya karte thay"
  23,68,To kya in logon ne kabhi is kalaam par gaur nahin kiya? Ya woh koi aisi baat laya hai jo kabhi inke aslaaf (forefathers) ke paas na aayi thi
  23,69,Ya yeh apne Rasool se kabhi ke waqif na thay ke (anjaana aadmi honay ke baais) ussey bidakte hain
  23,70,"Ya ye is baat ke qayal hain ke woh majnoon [possessed (by a jinn)] hai? Nahin, balke woh haqq laya hai aur haqq hi inki aksariyat (most) ko nagawar hai"
  23,71,"Aur haqq agar kahin inki khwaishaat ke peechey chalta to zameen aur aasman aur inki saari aabaadi ka nizam darham barham ho jata. Nahin, balke hum unka apna hi zikar unke paas laaye hain aur woh apne zikr se mooh moad rahey hain"
  23,72,Kya tu insey kuch maang raha hai? Tere liye tere Rubb ka diya hi behtar hai aur woh behtareen raziq hai
  23,73,Tu to unko seedhey raaste ki taraf bula raha hai
  23,74,Magar jo log aakhirat ko nahin maante woh raah e raast se hat kar chalna chahte hain
  23,75,Agar hum inpar reham karein aur woh takleef jis mein aaj kal yeh mubtila hain door kardein to yeh apni sarkashi mein bilkul hi behak jayenge
  23,76,"Inka haal to yeh hai ke humne unhein takleef mein mubtila kiya, phir bhi yeh apne Rubb ke aagey na jhuke aur na aajizi (humble)ikhtiyar karte hain"
  23,77,Albatta jab naubat yahan tak pahunch jayegi ke hum inpar sakht azaab ka darwaza khol denge to yakayak tum dekhoge ke us halat mein ye har khair se mayous hain
  23,78,"Woh Allah hi to hai jisne tumhein sunney aur dekhne ki quwwatein di aur sochne ko dil diye , magar tum log kam hi shukarguzar hotey ho"
  23,79,"Wahi hai jisne tumhein zameen mein phaylaya, aur usi ki taraf tum sametay jaogey"
  23,80,"Wahi zindagi bakashta hai aur wahi maut deta hai, gardish e layl (raat) o nahar (din) usi ke qabze qudrat mein hai. Kya tumhari samajh mein yeh baat nahin aati"
  23,81,Magar yeh log wahi kuch kehte hain jo unke peshraw (forefathers) keh chuke hain
  23,82,Yeh kehte hain “kya jab hum marr kar mitti ho jayenge aur haddiyon ka panjar ban kar reh jayenge to humko phir zinda karke uthaya jayega
  23,83,Humne bhi yeh wadey bahut sunay hain aur humse pehle hamare baap dada bhi suntey rahey hain. Yeh mehaz afasana haye pareena hain(ancient tales)”
  23,84,"Insey kaho, batao agar tum jaante ho, ke yeh zameen aur iski saari aabaadi kiski hai"
  23,85,"Yeh zaroor kahenge ke Allah ki, kaho phir tum hosh mein kyun nahin aatey"
  23,86,"Insey pucho, saato (seven) aasmaano aur arsh-e-azeem ka maalik kaun hai"
  23,87,"Yeh zaroor kahenge Allah, kaho phir tum darte kyun nahin"
  23,88,"Insey kaho, batao agar tum jaante ho ke har cheez par iqtedaar kiska hai? Aur kaun hai woh jo panaah deta hai aur uske muqable mein koi panaah nahin de sakta"
  23,89,"Yeh zaroor kahenge ke yeh baat to Allah hi keliye hai. Kaho, phir kahan se tumko dhoka lagta hai"
  23,90,"Jo amr e haqq hai woh hum inke saamne le aaye hain, aur koi shakk nahin ke yeh log jhotey hain"
  23,91,"Allah ne kisi ko apni aulaad nahin banaya hai aur koi dusra khuda uske saath nahin hai. Agar aisa hota to har khuda apni khalq ko lekar alag ho jaata, aur phir woh ek dusre par chadh daudte.Paak hai Allah un baaton se jo yeh log banate hain"
  23,92,"Khule aur chupe ka jaanne wala, woh baalatar hai us shirk se jo yeh log tajweez kar rahey hain"
  23,93,"(Aey Muhammad) dua karo ke “parwardigar, jis azaab ki inko dhamki di jaa rahi hai woh agar meri maujoodgi mein tu laye"
  23,94,"To aey mere Rubb, mujhey in zaalim logon mein shamil na kijiyo”"
  23,95,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke hum tumhari aankhon ke saamne hi woh cheez le aane ki poori qudrat rakhte hain jiski dhamki hum unhein de rahey hain
  23,96,"(Aey Nabi), burayi ko is tareeqe se dafa karo jo behtareen ho jo kuch baatein woh tumpar banate hain woh humein khoob maloom hai"
  23,97,"Aur dua karo ke “parwardigar, main shayateen ki uksahaton(waswason) se teri panaah maangta hoon"
  23,98,"Balke aey mere Rubb, main to issey bhi teri panaah maanga hoon ke woh mere paas aayein”"
  23,99,"(yeh log apni karni se baaz na aayenge) yahan tak ke jab in mein se kisi ko maut aa jayegi to kehna shuru kardega ke “Aey mere Rubb, mujhey usi duniya mein wapas bhej dijiye jisey main chodh aaya hoon"
  23,100,"Umeed hai ke ab main neik amal karunga”. Hargiz nahin, yeh to bas ek baat hai jo woh bakk raha hai. Ab in sab (marne waalon) ke peechey ek barzakh (barrier) hayal hai dusri zindagi ke din tak"
  23,101,"Phir junhi ke Sur (trumphet) phoonk diya gaya, unke darmiyan phir koi rishta na rahega aur na woh ek dusre ko puchenge"
  23,102,Us waqt jinke padle (scales) bhari hongey wahi falaah payenge
  23,103,Aur jinke padle (scales) halke honge wahi log hongey jinhon ne apne aap ko ghatay mein daal liya. Woh jahannum mein hamesha rahenge
  23,104,Aag unke chehron ki khaal chaat jayegi aur unke jabde (jaws) bahar nikal aayenge
  23,105,“kya tum wahi log nahin ho ke meri aayat tumhein sunayi jati thi to tum unhein jhutlate thay?”
  23,106,"Woh kahenge “aey hamare Rubb, hamari badbakhti hum par chaa gayi thi, hum waqayi gumraah log thay"
  23,107,"Aey parwardigar, ab humein yahan se nikaal de phir hum aisa kasoor karein to zaalim hongey”"
  23,108,"Allah taala jawab dega “ door ho mere saamne se, padey raho isi mein aur mujhse baat na karo"
  23,109,"Tum wahi log to ho ke mere kuch banday jab kehte thay ke aye hamare parwardigar, hum iman laye, humein maaf karde, humpar reham kar, tu sab raheemon se accha raheem hai"
  23,110,"To tumne unka mazaaq bana liye, yahan tak ke unki zidd ne tumhein yeh bhi bhula diya ke main bhi koi hoon, aur tum unpar haste rahey"
  23,111,Aaj unke us sabr ka maine yeh phal diya hai ke wahi kamiyaab hain”
  23,112,"Phir Allah taala unse puchega “batao,zameen mein tum kitne saal rahey?”"
  23,113,"Woh kahenge “ ek din ya din ka bhi kuch hissa hum wahan thehre hain, shumaar karne walon se pooch lijiye”"
  23,114,"Irshad hoga “ thodi hi dair thehre ho na, kaash tumne yeh us waqt jana hota"
  23,115,Kya tumne yeh samajh rakkha tha ke humne tumhein fizul(bekar) hi paida kiya hai aur tumhein hamari taraf kabhi palatna hi nahin hai?”
  23,116,"Pas baala o bartar hai Allah , baadshah e haqiqi, koi khuda uske siwa nahin, maalik hai arsh e buzurg ka"
  23,117,"Aur jo koi Allah ke saath kisi aur maabood ko pukare, jiske liye uske paas koi daleel nahin, to uska hisaab uske Rubb ke paas hai. Aisey kafir kabhi falaah nahin paa sakte"
  23,118,"(Aey Muhammad) kaho, “Mere Rubb darguzar farma, aur reham kar, aur tu sab raheemon se accha raheem hai”"